{"name":"Portobello Mushroom Pizzas","slug":"portobello-mushroom-pizzas","description":"","ingredients":[{"name":"large portobello mushrooms","quantity":"4","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"olive oil","quantity":"3 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Pizza Seasoning or Marinara Sauce Mix","quantity":"1 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"small green bell pepper","quantity":"1","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Marinara Sauce","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"diced tomatoes","quantity":"1 can (28 oz/796 ml)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"crushed tomatoes","quantity":"1 can (28 oz/796 ml)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Marinara Sauce Mix","quantity":"3 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"grated mozzarella cheese","quantity":"<sup>3</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null}],"totalTime":"20 min","servings":"4 servings","preparation":"<ol>\n  <li>Preheat oven to 400° F. Line <a data-item-id=\"423693c7-df9f-4960-8715-f08b2d79dead\" href=\"\">Sheet Pan</a> with <a data-item-id=\"457bbcd8-77a0-4a70-96c9-951018a3fc9c\" href=\"\">Sheet Pan Liner</a>.</li>\n  <li>Remove mushroom stems and use a spoon to scrape out and discard gills. Place mushroom caps in <a data-item-id=\"bd092c36-a4ba-5b73-9abc-fa95c0102e9a\" href=\"\">Multipurpose Steamer</a>. Drizzle with oil and sprinkle with seasoning; gently toss to coat. Cover and microwave on high 4 min.</li>\n  <li>Meanwhile, dice pepper.</li>\n  <li>When mushrooms are cooked, place on pan with underside of caps facing up. Divide sauce, cheese, and pepper between caps. Bake 8–10 min, or until cheese is bubbly.</li>\n</ol>","tags":[{"slug":"steamers","name":"Steamers"},{"slug":"epic_life_lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"low_sodium","name":"Low-sodium"},{"slug":"sugar_conscious","name":"Sugar Conscious"},{"slug":"dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"vegetarian","name":"Vegetarian"},{"slug":"gluten_free_e8446d0","name":"Gluten-free"},{"slug":"sheet_pan_3e5bebd","name":"Sheet Pan"},{"slug":"epic_life_dinner","name":"Dinner"}],"nutritionalInformation":{"servingSize":"","calories":210,"fat":16,"saturatedFat":5,"transFat":0,"cholesterol":20,"sodium":280,"carbohydrate":11,"fiber":3,"sugars":5,"protein":8},"tips":"<p>Try this recipe with your favourite pizza toppings!</p>"}